00:04:40.100 --> 00:04:40.996
This second's gone.

00:04:40.996 --> 00:04:42.620
We're just left with
meters per second.

00:04:42.620 --> 00:04:44.580
Eight meters per second.

00:04:44.580 --> 00:04:49.490
Or this is the same thing as
