that we would have traveled.

00:05:54.250 --> 00:05:56.630
Now we know from the last
video that distance is just

00:05:56.630 --> 00:05:59.970
the area under this
curve right over here.

00:05:59.970 --> 00:06:03.440
So it's just the area
under this curve.

00:06:03.440 --> 00:06:05.870
You say wait, this is kind of
a strange shape right here.

00:06:05.870 --> 00:06:07.540
How do I calculate its area?

00:06:07.540 --> 00:06:09.470
And we can just use a
little simple geometry

00:06:09.470 --> 00:06:11.790
to break it down into
two different areas, that

00:06:11.790 --> 00:06:14.740
are very easy to
calculate their areas.

00:06:14.740 --> 00:06:16.000
Or two simple shapes.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:18.950
You can break it down into
this blue part, this rectangle

00:06:18.950 --> 00:06:20.510
right over here.

00:06:20.510 --> 00:06:22.670
Easy to figure out the
area of a rectangle.

00:06:22.670 --> 00:06:25.030
And we could break it down
into this purple part.

00:06:25.030 --> 00:06:26.490
This triangle right here.

00:06:26.490 --> 00:06:28.920
Easy to figure out the
area of a triangle.

00:06:28.920 --> 00:06:30.890
And that will be the
total distance we travel.

00:06:30.890 --> 00:06:33.330
And even this will hopefully
make some intuition.

00:06:33.330 --> 00:06:36.000
Because this blue
area is how far would

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:38.470
we have traveled if we
were not accelerating.

00:06:38.470 --> 00:06:42.330
If we just went five meters
per second, for four seconds.

00:06:42.330 --> 00:06:44.192
So if you go five meters
per second times--

00:06:44.192 --> 00:06:46.400
so this is one second, two
second, three second, four

00:06:46.400 --> 00:06:47.320
second.

00:06:47.320 --> 00:06:51.020
So you're going from
times zero to time four,

00:06:51.020 --> 00:06:54.020
your change in time
is four seconds.

00:06:54.020 --> 00:06:57.330
So if you go five meters per
second, for four seconds,

00:06:57.330 --> 00:06:59.610
you're going to go 20 meters.

00:06:59.610 --> 00:07:02.360
This right here is 20 meters.

00:07:02.360 --> 00:07:04.040
That is the area
of this right here.

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:06.840
Five times four.

00:07:06.840 --> 00:07:09.750
This purple or
magenta area tells you

00:07:09.750 --> 00:07:12.040
how further than
this, are you going,

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:14.050
because you are
accelerating, because you

00:07:14.050 --> 00:07:16.840
kept going faster and
faster and faster.

00:07:16.840 --> 00:07:19.400
And it's pretty easy
to calculate this area.

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:22.850
The base here is still
five, because that's

00:07:22.850 --> 00:07:24.090
five seconds have gone by.

00:07:24.090 --> 00:07:25.750
And what's the height here?

00:07:25.750 --> 00:07:28.740
The height here is
my final velocity

00:07:28.740 --> 00:07:30.275
minus my initial velocity.

00:07:33.590 --> 00:07:38.240
Or it's the change in velocity
due to the acceleration.

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:40.860
And the change in velocity
due to the acceleration.

00:07:40.860 --> 00:07:43.200
13 minus five is eight.

00:07:43.200 --> 00:07:44.810
Or it's this 8 right over here.

00:07:44.810 --> 00:07:48.300
It is eight meters per second.

00:07:48.300 --> 00:07:51.290
So this height right over here
is eight meters per second.

00:07:51.290 --> 00:07:54.720
The base right over
here is four seconds.

00:07:54.720 --> 00:07:56.320
That's the time that past.

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:59.230
So what's the area
of this triangle?

00:07:59.230 --> 00:08:02.760
Area of a triangle is
one half, times the base,

00:08:02.760 --> 00:08:07.000
which is four seconds,
times the height, which

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:10.570
is eight meters per second.

00:08:10.570 --> 00:08:11.940
Seconds cancel out.

00:08:11.940 --> 00:08:14.540
One half times four
is two, times eight

00:08:14.540 --> 00:08:21.130
is equal to 16 meters.

00:08:21.130 --> 00:08:24.850
So the total distance we
traveled is 20 plus 16,

00:08:24.850 --> 00:08:27.090
is 36 meters.

00:08:27.090 --> 00:08:30.250
That is the total, or I could
say the total displacement,

00:08:30.250 --> 00:08:33.010
and once again, it's to the
right, since it is positive.

00:08:33.010 --> 00:08:35.590
So this is our displacement.

