00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:44.000
But I want you to
understand it it's

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:46.100
a completely intuitive
formula, and it just

00:08:46.100 --> 00:08:49.400
comes out of the logical
flow of reasoning

00:08:49.400 --> 00:08:51.410
that we went through
