00:08:51.410 --> 00:08:52.670
What is the area?

00:08:52.670 --> 00:08:56.320
Once again, if we just
think about the variables.

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:58.790
Well, the area of
this rectangle right

00:08:58.790 --> 00:09:03.100
here is our initial velocity,
times our change in time.

