We have to take it by half
because a triangle is only half

00:09:38.690 --> 00:09:40.020
of that rectangle.

00:09:40.020 --> 00:09:41.280
So times one half.

00:09:44.590 --> 00:09:46.320
And so this is the area.

00:09:46.320 --> 00:09:47.560
This is the purple area.

00:09:47.560 --> 00:09:49.160
That's not purple.

